	InsertBtnCtrl

textbox: create as edit mode
click on textbox in a selected slide -> drag mode
dbclick on a textbox in a selected slide -> edit mode
dbclick on a drag mode textbox -> edit mode
dbclick on a edit mode textbox -> drag mode
click on a slide -> all textboxes turn into display mode
click on the canvas -> all textboxes turn into display mode
if zoomin zoomout -> all textboxes turn into display mode